description:
Burdens is a hardcore/Punk/Metal band from the Philly suburbs. 
blind world savage death burdens hardcore harvcore metal punk rock from PennsylvaniaFor those of you who don't know, we've recently had some changes in our lineup. Jared is leaving the band to go to school at Full Sail in Florida. Chris has taken over on vocals and our friend Nick Cole will be taking over on guitar.

We are excited to announce that we will be releasing a new 7&quot; on Harvcore Records this Winter. It will be titled &quot;You Can't Save Us All&quot; and will feature 5 new songs. We just posted a new song titled &quot;Bad Luck&quot;
